 |                   King of Fighters 2003 and 2002                     |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 |  Company....: SNK                  |  Genre...: Fighting             |
 |  Released...: September 1st, 2005  |  Origin..: NTSC - Usa           |
 |  Media Type.: Dvd                  |  Fit on..: 2 Dvds               |
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 |                                                                      |
 | iNFO:                                                                |
 | -----                                                                |
 | This "Greatest Hits" collection of the most famous fighting          |
 | franchise is the 8th installment of the series and brings together   |
 | the greatest SNK characters of all time and the much heralded 3 on 3 |
 | fighting system.                                                     |
 |                                                                      |
 | * Revised 3 on 3 battles originally made famous in the KOF series    |
 |   from 1994-1998                                                     |
 |                                                                      |
 | * Easier and more evolved Max Power System. Stockpile your power and |
 |   use the Max Power system, for extreme damage                       |
 |                                                                      |
 | * 39 of the most popular characters plus additional secret           |
 |   characters                                                         |
 |                                                                      |
 | * All new over-the-top Special Moves!                                |
 |                                                                      |
 | * Exclusive bonus game system and characters for the Xbox            |
 |                                                                      |
